name: Yoga girl
description: This is a picture of a girl who’s been doing yoga for years. Through yoga, she found faith, let go of her fears, fell in love. Yoga cures her illness, keeps her in shape, inspires her. Which is why I decided to make this picture look like X-ray. I mean, yoga is how she gets to the bottom of her soul, and I hope I get to the bottom of my viewer’s soul through the photo.
